Provides a coherent interface and implementation for creating grouped date classes. This package is part of the RECON (<https://www.repidemicsconsortium.org/>) toolkit for outbreak analysis.

name: r-grates
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.3.0' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-grates
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/grates_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/grates/grates_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 11cb295d91388264ba93e57b952739005383cc5c5eb1cf811d5beafc9d818f79

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip  # [win]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-clock
    - r-ellipsis
    - r-rlang
    - r-vctrs

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-clock
    - r-ellipsis
    - r-rlang
    - r-vctrs

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('grates')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('grates')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://www.reconverse.org/grates/
  dev_url: https://github.com/reconverse/grates
  license: MIT
  summary: Provides a coherent interface and implementation for creating grouped date classes.
    This package is part of the RECON (<https://www.repidemicsconsortium.org/>) toolkit
    for outbreak analysis.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - thewchan
